  "content": "<p data-pid=\"UHqPhWje\">此合集（非我整理）收录了 Animenz 曾在 Sheet.host 公开的所有钢琴谱（现已删除），并整合了其他网友二次扒谱的作品。下载链接如下：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/user-attachments/files/17853797/All.Sheets.of.Animenz.zip\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"All Sheets of Animenz.zip\" data-draft-cover=\"\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">All Sheets of Animenz.zip</a><p data-pid=\"e6bQmsuz\">其中，鸟之诗钢琴谱在“Key 社组曲”中，文件名为 <code>Key anime piano suite v2.pdf</code>。打开文件，迎面而来的便是鸟之诗。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-15c17fedcb8f7e18a30446a7d095c633_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1162\" data-rawheight=\"795\" data-original-token=\"v2-8334ca1b8ac1dc5352a9f9cbdcfd5c3b\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1162\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-15c17fedcb8f7e18a30446a7d095c633_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1162&#39; height=&#39;795&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1162\" data-rawheight=\"795\" data-original-token=\"v2-8334ca1b8ac1dc5352a9f9cbdcfd5c3b\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1162\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-15c17fedcb8f7e18a30446a7d095c633_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-15c17fedcb8f7e18a30446a7d095c633_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p></p>",
